block content

  p Looking at how we create scenarios, storyboards, and wireframes from a persona.
  span#more
  +caption("User persona example, inspired by [Bin collection, BBC](https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-47170939)")
    include caption1.html
  h2 Observations
  ul
    li
      p Discusses the role of an average bin collector in a city
    li
      p The current system is inefficient
      ul
        li
          | Information on bin capacity is non-existant so all bins must be checked for
          | litter
        li Time is wasted on empty bins meaning routes may not be completed
    li
      p The council wants to add sensors to bins
      ul
        li
          | Only bins that require collection will be scheduled, optimising the
          | collection process
        li Workload is reduced for bin men
        li General public will shut the fuck up
        li
          | Local council save money on wages for scheduling roles and
          | complaints-handling
