  h2 Scenario
  ol
    li James, a 28-year-old bin man, has gotten ready for work
    li He carries everyday items, such as his phone, and his keys for his work van
    li He checks which bins need collecting and starts his route
  h2 Goals
  ul
    li Functionality
      ul
        li Remotely accessible: it&#39;s a job on the move
        li Available without internet connection: may not always have a connection
    li Context factors
      ul
        li Events around the city: can additional bin-usage be expected&#x2F;predicted?
    li Usability goals
      ul
        li Easy to read on the move
    li UX goals
      ul
        li Reliable
